				<h3>Taking us to places we don’t normally go</h3>
				<p>Our work began at the Mojave Spaceport, interviewing scientists, engineers and taking a first step towards understanding XCOR’s approach to space travel. There is a focus on safety and reliability in every part they craft – their engines have been redefining rocketry for over a decade. Creating an authentic and resonant brand required an understanding of their philosophy, technology and audience.</p>
				<p>Our designers poured through existing research while conducting field research, image studies, mood boards, wireframes and motion experiments. Our findings revealed the unexpected - we needed an entirely new kind of experiential lens to share the uniqueness of spaceflight.</p>
