				<h3>Shaping a brand with new tools</h3>
				<p>MU/DAI’s work is guided by practical innovation - a belief that great experiences are built with practicality. Virtual reality is a lens to places people don’t normally have access and in the case of space travel an incredibly practical tool. Space flight simulators are large, static machines with limited flexibility. Our Oculus Rift VR prototype created an experience that anyone can gain access to with an internet connection, a PC and a basic VR headset - lowering the barrier to space once more.</p>
